ocation = Lake Mary, Florida | title = The Stripper Who Found True Love |last = Donnally |first =  Ed | date = 2007-07 | accessdate = 2015-08-08 | archivedate = 2015-06-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150630233436/http://www.charismamag.com/life/145-j15/features/transformed-lives/2284-the-stripper-who-found-true-love | url = http://www.charismamag.com/life/145-j15/features/transformed-lives/2284-the-stripper-who-found-true-love}}</ref>。组织成员[[传福音|传福音]]的地点包括成人娱乐展会及[[脱衣舞俱乐部|脱衣舞俱乐部]]<ref name="Grecco-2007">{{cite book | title = Naked Ambition: An R Rated Look at an X Rated Industry | author = Grecco, Michael | year = 2007 | publisher = Rock Out Books | location = San Francisco | isbn = 0979331404 | page = n.p.}}</ref>。

